    <h3 id="overview">Overview</h3>
    <p>As product designer my role was to take new business and technological opportunities and make them available for our editors to work with. I created instruments, methodologies, and interfaces, and translated the needs to our development team, thus improving our products every day.</p>
    <ul class="sheet">
      <li><strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://www.archdaily.com/">https://www.archdaily.com/</a></li>
